data.description: 1 story home for sale in desirable Mira Lagos!  You will not want to miss the opportunity to purchase this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 3 car garage Bloomfield home with elegant wood flooring and spacious layout.  Highlighted features include a Rain Soft water filtration system with additional osmosis filter under kitchen sink, and built in drawers under the cabinets in the kitchen, bathrooms and laundry room.  This well kept 1 story corner lot home also features tinted living room windows in certain areas, double oven, beautiful master bathroom with bidet toilet feature and shower bench.  Enjoy your backyard with a bigger lot that wraps around to the side, and present with a back patio with sturdy covering to enjoy relaxing evenings and entertaining.
